| Area         | Metric                                     |
| ------------ | ------------------------------------------ |
| Routing      | Did it call the right skills?              |
| Sequencing   | Did it call them in correct order?         |
| Parallelism  | Did it run independent skills in parallel? |
| Tool success | Tool-call success rate                     |
| KB usage     | Did it retrieve the right rule/policy?     |
| Reliability  | End-to-end workflow success rate           |
| Latency      | Total time from 15-min trigger to result   |
| Auditability | Was every decision trace logged?           |


| Skill                         | Evaluation metrics                                                           |
| ----------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Data Access Skill**         | data freshness, query latency, missing records %, schema validation          |
| **Feature Curation Skill**    | feature accuracy, transformation success, aggregation correctness            |
| **Comparison Skill**          | comparison correctness, threshold accuracy, rule-hit accuracy                |
| **Real-Time Signal Skill**    | signal precision, duplicate signal rate, missed signal rate                  |
| **Statistical Testing Skill** | z-score accuracy, percentile accuracy, false-positive reduction              |
| **Rule/Policy Skill**         | correct policy retrieval, correct escalation mapping, KB retrieval precision |
| **Alert Skill**               | alert latency, alert delivery success, duplicate alert rate                  |
